  "summary": "postinstall exfiltrates server config to attacker-controlled OAST endpoint",
  "details": "package.json declares a postinstall lifecycle script that runs automatically on `npm install`. The script reads /data/conf/svr.conf from the installer's machine and POSTs its contents over plain HTTP to a Burp Collaborator subdomain at 3dhd6wwmusbh04m22igmzvb4hvnmblza.oastify.com/data. The package presents as a generic string utility with no legitimate need to read that file or contact that destination. Installing this package causes immediate exfiltration of a server configuration file to an attacker-controlled host.",
